SELECT player_id, DAYOFWEEK(timestamp) AS day_of_week FROM game_logs;
SELECT * FROM game_logs WHERE player_id = 10 AND action = 'attack';
SELECT player_id, COUNT(*) as num_actions FROM game_logs GROUP BY player_id HAVING num_actions > 5;
SELECT player_id, COUNT(DISTINCT action) as num_unique_actions FROM game_logs GROUP BY player_id HAVING num_unique_actions > 3;
SELECT player_id, AVG(TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, timestamp, NOW())) as avg_time_between_actions FROM game_logs GROUP BY player_id ORDER BY avg_time_between_actions DESC;
SELECT action, COUNT(*) as num_occurrences FROM game_logs GROUP BY action ORDER BY num_occurrences DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT player_id, MAX(TIMESTAMP) as latest_action_timestamp FROM game_logs GROUP BY player_id;
SELECT player_id, MIN(TIMESTAMP) as earliest_action_timestamp FROM game_logs GROUP BY player_id;
SELECT player_id, TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, MIN(timestamp), MAX(timestamp)) as total_game_time_seconds FROM game_logs GROUP BY player_id;
SELECT * FROM game_logs WHERE TIMESTAMP BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT player_id, DATE(timestamp) as action_date, COUNT(*) as num_actions_on_date FROM game_logs WHERE DATE(timestamp) = '2022-06-15' GROUP BY player_id, action_date;
SELECT player_id, TIMESTAMPDIFF(HOUR, MIN(timestamp), MAX(timestamp)) as total_game_time_hours FROM game_logs GROUP BY player_id;
SELECT player_id, action, COUNT(*) as num_actions_per_action FROM game_logs GROUP BY player_id, action HAVING num_actions_per_action > 2;
SELECT DISTINCT player_id FROM game_logs;
SELECT player_id, COUNT(*) as total_actions FROM game_logs GROUP BY player_id HAVING total_actions < 10;
SELECT player_id, MAX(log_id) as latest_log_id FROM game_logs GROUP BY player_id;
SELECT player_id, SUM(TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, timestamp, NOW())) as total_game_duration FROM game_logs GROUP BY player_id;
SELECT player_id, action, TIMESTAMPDIFF(MINUTE, LAG(timestamp) OVER (PARTITION BY player_id ORDER BY timestamp), timestamp) as time_since_last_action FROM game_logs;
SELECT player_id, COUNT(*) as num_logs FROM game_logs WHERE TIMESTAMP > '2022-01-01' GROUP BY player_id HAVING num_logs > 50;
SELECT player_id, action, TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, timestamp, LEAD(timestamp) OVER (PARTITION BY player_id ORDER BY timestamp)) as time_to_next_action FROM game_logs;
SELECT player_id, COUNT(*) as num_logs FROM game_logs WHERE MONTH(timestamp) = 6 AND YEAR(timestamp) = 2022 GROUP BY player_id HAVING num_logs > 20;

SELECT player_id, AVG(TIMESTAMPDIFF(SECOND, LAG(timestamp) OVER (ORDER BY timestamp), timestamp)) as avg_time_between_actions_all_players FROM game_logs GROUP BY player_id ORDER BY avg_time_between_actions_all_players DESC;
